    <item>
      <title>亨特·拜登改变立场，提出私下作证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/hunter-biden-reverses-stance-offering-to-testify-in-private</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亨特·拜登突然改变了他对众议院共和党弹劾调查人员的蔑视，在坚称他只会公开回答他们的问题后，主动提出私下在他们面前作证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/hunter-biden-reverses-stance-offering-to-testify-in-private</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 21:28:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾选举新领导人受到世界密切关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/taiwan-picks-new-leader-in-election-closely-watched-by-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾选民即将参加选举，这场选举将决定台湾未来几年与华盛顿和北京的关系，并影响地区安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/taiwan-picks-new-leader-in-election-closely-watched-by-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称奥斯汀犯了错误，但仍然对五角大楼负责人有信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/biden-says-austin-erred-in-hospital-flap-but-retains-confidence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，在国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀几天未能通知白宫他已住院的事件发生后，他对国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀保持了信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/biden-says-austin-erred-in-hospital-flap-but-retains-confidence</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 20:52:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登认为胡塞武装应被视为恐怖组织</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/biden-thinks-houthis-should-be-considered-terrorist-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登表示，他认为袭击红海航运的也门胡塞武装是恐怖组织。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/biden-thinks-houthis-should-be-considered-terrorist-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 20:39:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和盟国准备应对胡塞武装对空袭的报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/allies-await-new-attacks-as-houthis-vow-retaliation-to-airtrikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[胡塞叛军誓言要以美国和英国商船为目标，一天前，胡塞盟国对也门胡塞武装发动空袭，引发人们对以色列-加沙战争正在演变成拜登政府担心的与伊朗的地区冲突的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/allies-await-new-attacks-as-houthis-vow-retaliation-to-airtrikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 19:54:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰图斯克表示，他将寻求调查央行行长的方法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/poland-s-tusk-says-will-seek-ways-to-probe-central-bank-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·图斯克表示，仍有调查央行行长亚当·格拉平斯基的余地，并称最近法院禁止立法者调查他的裁决“不具约束力”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/poland-s-tusk-says-will-seek-ways-to-probe-central-bank-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 19:51:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普因视频电话宣传赢得 2018 年诉讼被驳回</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/trump-wins-dismissal-of-2018-lawsuit-over-video-phone-promotions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着一项审判被搁置，另一项审判将于下周开始，前总统唐纳德·特朗普在一场低调的诉讼中悄然取得了胜利，这场诉讼已经持续了五年多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/trump-wins-dismissal-of-2018-lawsuit-over-video-phone-promotions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 18:12:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
